Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Those locusts must've eaten up \Nall the rice before it was harvested.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked the neighboring villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Some have had their fields \Noverrun by rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All are suffering \Nfrom some form of misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Some villages have even been struck  \N by epidemics.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:01:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Those near the borders are hit the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be spreading inwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be the demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we couldn't kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We must find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Hall of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you spare a morsel of food \Nfor this child?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.05,0:01:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that good, Sakichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still more. Chew well now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise you as the man \Nwho looks over this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forsake you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:26.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,酷い…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:33.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのバッタどもに収穫前の稲や作物を残らず食い尽くされたのであろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:34.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:38.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,近隣の村々を見てまいりました
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:40.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうであった？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:46.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ネズミに田畑を食い荒らされるなど、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:50.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,原因は違えどどの村も災難に見舞われております
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:57.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,流行り病に冒された村もあり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:01:01.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,国境にある土地ほど被害は酷く、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:03.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,徐々に領内に広まっているようです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:07.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱり…鬼神の仕業かな…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:10.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺たちがあいつを討ち損ねたから…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:18.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,確かめねばなるまい。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:20.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,地獄堂へ行くぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:22.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お慈悲でございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:29.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうか…この子に、\Nひとかけらの食べ物でも分けちゃあもらえませんでしょうか！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.05,0:01:43.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うめぇか？サキチ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:47.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだまだあっからよぉ…よく噛んで食えぇ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:50.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この地を治める者として約束しよう…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:53.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,決してそなたたちを見捨てはせぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayed this world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And it simmers within
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupturing my innards
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Swelling a reddish black
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the sun burnt skin ruptures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the seething darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:03:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,#20 The story of the Nue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's all bright red \Neverywhere I look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here to defeat a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like lots of people \Nhave been killed around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny. I've been to the mountains  \N in the fall before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I so amazed now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I was too busy trying to stay alive  \N to notice when I was on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro got me some food...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There are four seasons, you see? \NSpring, summer, fall, and winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, it's fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In the fall, \Nthe mountains turn bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But not red like the color of demons, \NI don't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes you feel so great \Njust gazing at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you call "beautiful."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I only just learned about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be able to see it some day. \NI know you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just mountains. Lots of \Nbeautiful stuff like the sun and clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just nodding. \NAre you really listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear more. More of your stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you really have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing like when I first met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a lot of stuff \NI want to tell you about, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, let's go beat that demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to kill the demon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dice-spot Saburota.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been hunting the demon \Nfor about 6 months now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty tough beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone after it many times, \Nwith only this to show for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so fixed on killing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It ate my ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in front of my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mama, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I've had an empty hole \Nright here ever since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Those arms. I see you've been through \Na lot with them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Must've been pretty frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes here on certain days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, bro is really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll avenge your mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck? Its body...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a jumble of animal parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you siding with the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't it kill your mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing the demon won't bring Ma back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm taking others' lives away instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I let this guy eat up \Neveryone that passes through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They all cry and plead for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only then \Nthat I don't feel empty in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is strange at the Hall of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the demon statues lets out \Nsomething like a heartbeat now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's faint, yet distinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt it, plain as day,  \N when the Goddess's head was smashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That among the 12 demons,  \N there was one that failed to eat my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the Goddess of Mercy is cracked,  \N your deal has been broken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The days of prosperity  \N for this land are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, we fell from that cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. I'll get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it'll come out in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, below you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't with those arms, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there, Ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we cross this mountain, \Nwe'll reach the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for \Nputting you through this, Saburota.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make a name for myself with \Nthis some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And we won't have to sell pelts anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make a good living for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Saburota.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburota...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburota...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring another.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I feed myself to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you'll break your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll find my way out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Move over a bit, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I heard a familiar voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a body?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you have an empty hole here too, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburota...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburota!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He left her to die, all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting like a samurai all the time, \Nbut what a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't, I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Saburota.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why don't you run for your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared? Scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry! Beg for your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not human. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like with the ghost fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He beat a demon, \Nbut isn't getting any body parts back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-Give it back! \N-Stop it, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bro, stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where my body is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One cannot escape one's fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a heavy burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it his fate to bear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:48.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すげー！どこもかしこも真っ赤っ赤だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉっといけね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:58.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここにはバケモンの退治に来たんだったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:01.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この辺りの山で何人も襲われてるらしいんだけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:23.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,変だな…秋の山なんて初めてじゃないのに。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでこんなに…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:36.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そっか…1人でいたときは生きてくだけで精一杯だったもんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらも食べよっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え…？おいらにくれんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:52.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろのぶん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:59.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきが…おいらに、食いモンを…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:11.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…季節にはな、春・夏・秋・冬ってあるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今は秋でな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:20.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,秋んなると山ん中が真っ赤に染まるんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:25.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,真っ赤って言っても、鬼神の色とは全然違うと思うぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:29.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見てるとなんとも言えずいい気分になるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そういうのを綺麗って言うんだよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:36.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらも…さっき知ったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきもいつか、きっと見えるようんなるさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:45.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,山だけじゃない。お陽さんとか雲とか、いろんな綺麗なもんがさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:50.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うんうんうんって…ホントに聞いてんのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからもっと聞きたい。どろろの話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:57.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんか変わったな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:04.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うん。やっぱり変わったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:06.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,出会った頃とは大違いだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:10.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらも…あにきと話したいことがいっぱいあんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:15.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも、まずはその前にバケモン退治だな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バケモンを探してんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだよあんた！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:21.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そう身構えんなって。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺もな、バケモンを殺しに来たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺は賽の目の三郎太ってんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:36.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,半年ほど前から、この山でヤツを狙ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手強いヤツでなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:43.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何度もやり合っちゃあ…この有り様よ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:48.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでそこまでして？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヤツにおっかぁを喰われたのよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,目の前でな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃんを…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:09.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今でも忘れられねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:18.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのときから…ココにぽっかりと穴が空いちまったようさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんた…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:29.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その腕、あんたもヤツらに手酷い目に遭わされたみてぇだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:33.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぞ恐ろしい思いをしたろう…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行こう。どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ヤツは決まった日にこの岩場に現れる。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今日がその日だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫。あにきは強いんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,必ずおっかちゃんの仇を討てるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ…頼りにしてるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:12.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,来る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:26.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な…なんだ…あの身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いろんなモンが混ざってらぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こっち来るな！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何やってんだよあんた！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:12.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,少しゃぁやるみてぇだなぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:14.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な…なんでバケモンと一緒にいんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そいつはおっかちゃんの仇だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:21.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バケモン殺したところで、おっかぁは帰っちゃ来ねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:25.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからよぉ…代わりにこっちが奪ってやるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:29.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,山を通りがかったヤツは、みんなこいつに喰わせたぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:33.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誰もが助けてくれって泣き叫んでよぉ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:38.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そいつを見てるときだきゃあ…ココが埋まる気がすんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんた…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:10.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿。地獄堂で妙なことが。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:16.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,時折、鬼神像の1つから鼓動のごとき音が響くのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:19.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かすかではありますが、間違いなく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:25.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの菩薩像が砕けたとき、はっきりと感じたのでございます。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:31.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,12の鬼神のうち、あの子を喰い損ねたものがいると。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:40.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,菩薩像が砕けた今、殿との約定は破れました。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:44.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この国の安寧の時は…終わりまする
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あに…き…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだ…おいらたち、あっこから落ちて…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:17.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:23.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでもねぇ！今起きるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:38.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:41.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,心配すんなって！そのうち抜けらぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,違う。下だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その腕じゃ無理だ、あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:06.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なら…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうすぐだぞ、おっかぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この山を越えれば、医者のいる町だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すまないねぇ…三郎太。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いずれ俺は、こいつで成り上がる。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:39.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そしたらもう、獣の皮なんぞ売る必要はねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,せいぜい楽させてやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,三郎太…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:57.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,三…郎太…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:02.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,三…郎太…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,次だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,次のやつを連れてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:26.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あるいは…俺を喰らうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:41.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ…！だ、ダメだって！壊れちまうよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきの大事な腕だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:47.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫、こんなの自力で抜け出してやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:56.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちょっくら…どいてくんな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:45.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞き覚えのある声がしたもんでねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,間に合って幸いだったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,身体が欲しいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:54.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺の…ものだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あに…き…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前生きてたのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:39.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なーんだ…お前もここに、穴が空いてんのか。ヘッ、だが…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,無駄よ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:11.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,三郎太…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,三郎太？あぁっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:35.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっ…そっ…そりゃ何だい！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:55.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見捨てて1人だけねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:58.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,武士の真似事なんぞして…いざとなったら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:02.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,がねぇ…んだ…しょうがねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行くぞ、三郎太。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,仇討ちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:18.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,助けてくれぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なーんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:32.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,みんなそうじゃねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:42.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめろぉー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:48.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ぐっ！なんでだよ！なんでおめぇは逃げねぇんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,怖ぇだろ！？なら叫べ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,泣いて命乞いしろぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:41.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前の…ように…なりたかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:51.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう…なれねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:22.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:08.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:10.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,返せ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前は…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:14.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,返せ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人じゃ…ないから…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:39.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,前の…化けギツネんときと一緒だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:43.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神を倒したのに、身体が戻らねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こいつは…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:05.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,返せぇ！\Nやめてくれよ！あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:07.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺の！身体だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:10.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こんなの…こんなの酷すぎるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若、あれを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:31.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:41.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう…やめてくれよ…あにき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:50.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どこ行くんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:52.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:56.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこに…俺の身体がある
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:59.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まっ…待ってくれよ！あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:12.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,背負った因果からは…逃れられねぇか…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:16.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんとも難儀なことだよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:20.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これもまた因果…か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Born into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The distorted shape of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it beats courageously
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from the path of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing the withering seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We search for the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In our ugliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.31,0:23:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even recognize the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As we peel back the skin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We are forever tormented by our stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the dawn never comes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the painful night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.12,0:23:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You who distrusts nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to love  \N this accursed world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.30,0:23:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we carry the world  \N on our shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nue"
